{"tid":789971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秀茂坪安泰邨男子墮樓　跌落籃球場死亡","createTime":"2018-08-22T15:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T10:39:11.000Z","uid":18213,"like":44,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ce4a2492ee75768c04ca7993f434e26718a175","tid":789971,"uid":18213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"秀茂坪安泰邨一名男子從高處墮下死亡，今日(22日)晚上9時46分，警方接獲一名男子報案，指其年約20多歲的兄長從在和泰樓高處墮下。警員及救護員隨即趕赴現場，發現墮樓男子倒臥於和泰樓對出一個籃球場重創，救護員作初步驗查後，證實該男子已死亡。警方以帳篷覆蓋死者遺體，而死者的親友亦趕至認屍，眾人神情哀傷，據悉，死者生前受感情問題困擾，墮樓前曾向親友發短訊，警方正作進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180822/bkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180822%2Fbkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001.html&d=wVF4sxI16Ui%2FQc7GR08yLXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2cc1feca\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180822/bkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180822/photo/bkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180822232314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180822%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180822224430266-0822_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180822232314&h=a5601f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b9f55a0d0e3dbb46ce31b7cb377b17840ec4b3","tid":789971,"uid":10692,"like":117,"dislike":4,"score":113,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:46:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51506aea1a7bc5fb580cd09560af76b73af3bf3e","tid":789971,"uid":132587,"